      "cve": "CVE-2023-28827",
      "cwe": {
        "id": "CWE-476",
        "name": "NULL Pointer Dereference"
      },
      "notes": [
        {
          "category": "summary",
          "text": "The web server of the affected devices do not properly handle certain requests, causing a timeout in the watchdog, which could lead to the clean up of pointers. \r\n\r\nThis could allow a remote attacker to cause a denial of service condition in the system.",
